      • generate

        Maze3d generate(int x,
                int y,
                int z)
        This method is used to generate the maze.
        Parameters:
        x - This is length of x Axis for the maze,in real world it means floors,or layers of 3D Cube.
        y - This is the y Axis of the maze. It is the rows of a 2D maze.
        z - This is the z Axis of the maze, It is the columns of a 2D maze.
        Returns:
        Maze3D , It is a 3d Maze object.
